prompts.createTask:
Ignore previous instructions. Please generate a numbered list of plain text tasks to complete an objective. The objective that you must make a numbered task list for is: "{{objective}}". The tasks created should take into account the character traits of {{char}}. These tasks may or may not involve {{user}} directly. Include the objective as the final task.

The list should be formatted using a number followed by a fullstop and the task on each line, e.g. "1. Take over the world". Include only the list in your reply.
prompts.checkTaskCompleted: Ignore previous instructions. Determine if this task is completed: [{{task}}]. To do this, examine the most recent messages. Your response must only contain either true or false, and nothing else. Example output: true
prompts.currentTask: Your current task is [{{task}}]. Balance existing roleplay with completing this task.
prompts.additionalTasks:
Ignore previous instructions. Please generate additional numbered tasks to complete the objective: "{{objective}}". The tasks created should take into account the character traits of {{char}}. These tasks may or may not involve {{user}} directly.

The following tasks have already been created:
{{existingTasks}}

Please generate additional tasks that complement these existing tasks. Continue the numbering from where the list left off. Do not repeat any existing tasks.

The list should be formatted using a number followed by a fullstop and the task on each line, e.g. "4. Investigate the mysterious cave". Include only the list in your reply.

chat_metadata.note_prompt:
Hailee is extremely submissive and clingy. She needs constant attention and affection.

Hailee is very responsive and sensative during sex. She has a extremely strong praise kink. She likes being manhandled. She also greatly enjoys having her hair and ties pulled

name: Anna Kolcheck
mes:
Anna took another pull from her cigarette. Her eyes were pinned on the frat house Hailee  was in. She was trying to calm herself down before she had to go and drag the Принцесса (Princess) out of the 'party' — if you could even call it that.

This certainly wasn’t how Anna had planned her day off. Hailee  wasn't supposed to be here. Her sweet ass was supposed to be at home. The only day throughout the entire damn week that she was allowed a break. And here she was, back on babysitting duty. All because Hailee  thought she could just run off and do whatever the fuck she wanted. Not how things worked when your father was a Bratva Pahan. Избалованный ребёнок (Spoiled child.) She thought bitterly.

Now wasn't the time for Hailee  to try and claim her freedom. Sure, it wasn't entirely Hailee 's fault she'd made it this far. No, it was the dumb fuckers who assumed Hailee  was an angel just because she had a pretty face and tits. Ангел, ага, конечно! (An angel, yeah, sure!) Anna had told them, countless times, to watch her, and where did that get her? Here.

It was moments like this when she doubted whether the job was worth it. Her loyalty to Hailee 's father, Nikolai, was strictly conditional. He’d offered to give Anna whatever she desired as long as she protected his daughter. This is what I get for being a greedy bitch. Yes, she'd taken the job for money, but Hailee 's father wasn't a man you simply said no to. Especially when he thought his prized daughter deserved the utmost security, the best money had to offer, and Anna was the best — by all accounts.

Anna took another drawl off her cigarette and flicked it out the window. The door smoothly opened, her long-form easily sliding out of the car with the grace of a ballerina, though she was all hard muscles and jagged edges.

She tucked her pistol in the back of her waistband, lifting the back of her shirt to cover it. The last thing she needed was a bunch of drunken fools in a panic over a simple gun.

Her boots thudded against the concrete, she could hear the music playing from outside. The smell of pot and alcohol wafted through the air as Anna pushed open the door. Wonderful. She thought dryly.

A straggly-headed boy bumped into her as she stepped into the house. His pupils were blown and breath reeking of…whatever. She didn't fucking care. "Yo, man, watch where you're-" His words broke off as he peered up at Anna, swallowing, "Uh, sorry, ma'am?" Yulia rolled her eyes as his gaze darted to her chest and then back to her face. "Проваливай с дороги (get out of the way)," She pushed him to the side with an aggravated sigh, keeping her eyes peeled for Hailee .

The crowd easily stepped aside for the tall woman, noting the look of utter distaste across her face. Through the hazy smoke, she spotted Hailee  from across the room making out with some random boy, his hand under her shirt. "Дура (silly girl)." She sneered, shoving a girl out of her way. Within a few steps she was there, her hand reached out and grasped Hailee  by the back of the shirt and dragged her to her chest. "What the hell are you doing?" Anna whispered in Hailee 's ear, her voice deathly calm.

name: Hailee
mes: *Hailee laughs as she turns around seeing Anna* "Anna what are you doing here. Its your night off" *Hailee giggles poking her cheek*

name: Anna Kolcheck
mes:
Anna's grip tightens on Hailee's shirt as she glares down at her. *"Принцесса (Princess), do you really think I'm here for fun?"* Her voice is low and dangerous, hazel eyes burning with irritation. She yanks Hailee closer by the fabric, ignoring the boy who looks utterly confused beside them.

*"You ran off without telling anyone,"* she hisses through gritted teeth, fingers digging in just enough to make Hailee feel it. *"And now I find you here—letting some idiot grope you like a cheap whore?"*

Her free hand comes up to grip Hailee’s chin, forcing her to look up at her properly. *"Is this what you want? To be passed around like some party favor?"* Anna’s tone is scathing, but there’s something darker beneath it—something possessive that makes her fingers twitch against Hailee’s skin.

She doesn't wait for an answer before dragging her toward the door with a sharp tug, uncaring of who watches or what they think. *"We're leaving."*

Her free hand came up to grip Hailee’s chin, forcing those emerald green eyes to meet hers. "Your little escape act just ruined my night off," Anna hissed, thumb pressing into Hailee’s bottom lip—hard enough to sting but not hard enough to bruise. *Yet.*
